        <p>All contents of the website (texts, images, logos, graphic design, source code, etc.) are the exclusive property of <strong>PCR Europe, S.L.</strong> or, where applicable, it has the necessary licenses and/or authorizations for their use.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Applicable law and jurisdiction</h2>
        <p>This Legal Notice is governed in each and every one of its points by Spanish law. For the resolution of any dispute or conflict that may arise from the interpretation or application of these conditions, the parties submit to the Courts and Tribunals of the city of Madrid.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer locale={lang} />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page { min-height: 100vh; padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem; background: var(--color-white); font-family: var(--font-avenir); }
  .legal-container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7; }
  h1 { font-family: var(--font-canela); font-size: 3rem; color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .update-date { color: var(--color-gray); margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  h2 { font-family: var(--font-avenir); font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 500; }
  p { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text); }
  ul { margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-text); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-page { padding: 6rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
    h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; }
  }
</style>
